snippet.textDisplay:
I hope at least one person will read this, and I wish you a beautiful day… 💖




My name is Lisa Schettner and I am a 22-year-old French & Czech singer-songwriter. I play the piano, the guitar, the tin whistle, the harp, and I love to dance. My life goal is to make people happy and inspire them through my music, and to create original soundtracks for movies. I post my own songs on my channel as well as covers.

It's a tough path to follow, as it is difficult to get recognition online nowadays without paid promotion. I'm planning to release a debut album this year with many songs, but for this I would need your support. If you have a moment, please check out one of my videos and let me know what you think. Every single view, like, comment... counts enormously.

Also, please give this comment a thumbs-up so that others can see it.

Thank you sooo much, and I cannot wait to read your comments. 😊 💋
